        <div><a name="_calendarera" id="_calendarera"></a><h2>6.2<span style="mso-tab-count:1">&#xA0; </span>CalendarEra</h2><p class="MsoNormal"><a name="_96130c0b-84c9-4641-aa46-169ebcbe6930" id="_96130c0b-84c9-4641-aa46-169ebcbe6930"></a>This represents a calendar era.</p><div class="Note"><a name="_3c77fee2-687c-4064-bf33-57fa05496e8f" id="_3c77fee2-687c-4064-bf33-57fa05496e8f"></a><p class="Note"><span class="note_label">NOTE</span><span style="mso-tab-count:1">&#xA0; </span>calendar eras within a calendar system may overlap, and is therefore
unnecessary to have an end reference date.</p></div>

